    base:desc "The ACC Controlling functional entity runs in the DT, determines the lead vehicle and computes a desired speed. The computed speed is packaged by the Data Translation FE and sent back to the vehicle over the same Wi‑Fi UDP link. On the physical side the Actuation FE receives the command and drives the motor and steering servo to achieve the requested speed. The documents do not detail command message schemas, authentication, conflict resolution, or explicit execution acknowledgments."
